Alpha Dolphy::

Alpha Dolphy was cheking all maximal's communications, it was one of 
her duties.

Alpha Dolphy was a nice femme. Her beast mode was a silver trasmetal 
dolphy with cyan-eyes. In beast mode she was tall and thin girl. Her 
trasmetallic skin in robot mode was silver and like her beast mode, 
in robot mode she had cyan eyes.

She usually was happy and Optimistic bot. But now she felt sad, she 
knew that one of Starjumper's crew was prisioner, and worst was that 
who caught him were Decepticons!! She heard horrible tales about 
them... well it was time to give the report, thought the femme


She opened her comm link towards the bridge "Err... Sir???" said the 
femme "Well I haven't any new about Condor, but computers are 
reporting something strange around follow coordinates 2-4-5 (Florida) 
and Khonkolor hasn't came back base..."
